cc:Work.dc:title: Open Source 2012 pocket calendar
cc:Work.dc:description:
A Open Source Pocket size calendar made in Inkscape. 
 
Special thanks to the plugin in EXTENSIONS > RENDER > Calendar 
 
The months are in Romanian , but it`s easy to translate. 
 
Let`s keep Open Source alive, let`s make everyday stuff that we use at the office available on Open Clip Art Library
